title: Golden Bears rally for Senior Night tie against Spartans
text: Thursday, October 15, 2015 - 2:34:04 PM Local Sports Golden Bears rally for Senior Night tie against Spartans 10/14/2015 (Updated 11:01:29 PM) The Vestal Golden Bears scored twice in the second half to force overtime in a 3-3 tie against visiting Maine-Endwell on Wednesday night. The game was senior night for the Golden Bears. Vestal next hosts JC in a STAC Semi-final on Saturday at 9am.
